        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid), over a medium-high heat</p><p>Chop the <strong>cherry\u00a0tomatoes</strong> in half</p>",
