            "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-creamy-chorizo-gnocchi-with-spinach/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>baby leaf spinach</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min or until the spinach begins to wilt</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/10-min-creamy-chorizo-gnocchi-with-spinach/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained gnocchi</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs further or until the sauce begins to stick to the gnocchi \u2013 this is your\u00a0<strong>creamy chorizo gnocchi</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy cooking water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
